4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in JavaScript and Python. The program spans 18 weeks, consisting of three weekly classes and a low teacher-to-student ratio of 1:7. Participants do not require prior coding knowledge, making it accessible to beginners. 

The curriculum includes web development, algorithm scripting, and app building, with a focus on hands-on experience through a final project. Upon completion, graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. 

